Description: A collection of useful functions and example code created and used 
  by the Schloss Lab for reproducible microbiome research. Do common tasks like 
  read mothur output files, tidy up your microbiome data, and format rmarkdown 
  documents for publication. 
  See the website <http://www.schlosslab.org/schtools/> for more information, 
  documentation, and examples.
